[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說八吉祥神呪經",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吳月氏優婆塞支謙譯",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞如是：一時，佛在羅閱祇耆闍崛山中，與千",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二百五十比丘俱，菩薩千人皆彌勒等。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b07_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告賢者舍利弗及諸比丘：",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b08_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「皆一心聽！",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b08_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告賢者舍利弗：",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「東方去是一恒沙，有佛名安隱囑累滿具足王如來、至真、無所著、最正覺，今現在說法，其世界名曰滿所願聚。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b11_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「去是二恒沙，有佛名紺琉璃具足王如來、無所著、最正覺，今現在說法，其世界名曰慈哀光明。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b13_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「去是三恒沙，有佛名勸助眾善具足王如來、無所著、最正覺，今現在說法，其世界名曰歡喜快樂。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b15_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「去是四恒沙，有佛名曰無憂德具足王如來、無所著、最正覺，今現在說法，其世界名曰一切樂入。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「去是五恒沙，有佛名藥師具足王如來、無所著、最正覺，今現在說法，其世界名曰滿一切珍寶法。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「去是六恒沙，有佛名曰蓮華具足王如來、無所著、最正覺，今現在說法，其世界名曰滿香名聞。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「去是七恒沙，有佛名算擇合會具足王如來、無所著、最正覺，今現在說法，其世界名曰一切解說音聲遠聞。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「去是八恒沙，有佛名解散一切縛具足王如來、無所著、最正覺，今現在說法，其世界名曰一切解脫。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告賢者舍利弗：",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072b28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此諸佛如來、無所著、過四道不受、最正覺，其國土清淨，無五濁、無愛欲、無意垢。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人，聞此八佛及國土名，受持奉行諷誦，廣為他人解說其義者，終不愚癡，口之所言，無有失誤，相好具足，無所缺減，無央數年不為乏少。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是人終不墮太山地獄、餓鬼、畜生中也，是人終不望取羅漢、辟支佛道而般泥洹，必當逮得無上平等之道，常遇陀隣尼，常行菩薩道，得功德無量。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c07_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「第一四天王常擁護之，不為縣官所拘錄，不為盜賊所中傷，不為天龍、鬼神所觸嬈，閱叉鬼神、蠱道鬼神、若人、若非人，皆不能害殺得其便也，除其宿命不請。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若有疾病、水火、烏鳴、惡夢、諸魔所嬈，恐怖衣毛竪時，常當讀是八吉祥神呪經呪之，即得除愈。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c13_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，佛說偈言：",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c13_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若有持是經，　　八佛國土名，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不墮三惡處，　　疾得無上道。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自覺發道意，　　見佛即開解，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "中外常歡喜，　　供養心恭敬。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "億劫阿僧祇，　　行惡悉消除，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "持是八吉祥，　　速得明解教。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "供事是經者，　　千葉華中生，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "珍寶為其出，　　色像好無上。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人聞是尊經，　　尊敬信樂者，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "奉持諷誦讀，　　清淨無放逸。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "女人信是經，　　敬慎無諛諂。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "棄女為男子，　　聰明常黠慧，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "奉持八佛名，　　出入賊不害。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "刀兵水火毒，　　諸邪不能干，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愛樂奉是經，　　諸魔不得便。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "鬼神諸官屬，　　無能嬈亂者，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0072c29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "飛行到諸剎，　　所在大豐樂。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心意正無邪，　　見佛大歡喜，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所生常遇佛，　　等心奉事之。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切眾惡除，　　疾得泥洹道，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "精進無懈怠，　　去離諸緣著。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為人朴直儒，　　奉持八佛名，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "勇猛降眾魔，　　其力如金剛。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "端正相好具，　　一切莫能當，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "布施無慳貪，　　巨億萬家生。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "盜賊及怨家，　　自然皆消除，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "疾病縣官事，　　烏鳴諸惡夢，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "持是八佛名，　　呪之即除愈。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "奉持是經者，　　彌勒菩薩等，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第一四天王，　　常共擁護之。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所願皆可得，　　踊躍大歡喜，",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一心信樂者，　　福德亦如是。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，諸菩薩：",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "颰陀和菩薩、羅憐那竭菩薩、橋曰兜菩薩、那羅達菩薩、須深彌菩薩、摩訶須和薩和菩薩、因祗達菩薩、和輪調菩薩，是八人求道已來無央數劫，於今未取佛，願言：",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「使十方天下、人民皆得佛道。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a21_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有急疾，皆當呼我八人名字，即得解脫；",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "壽命欲終時，我八人便當飛往迎逆之。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」諸菩薩彌勒等、第一四天王，皆白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「吾當擁護持八吉祥神呪經者，與我并力令諸疾病皆得除愈。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a25_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說經已，舍利弗、彌勒菩薩，及諸比丘、天龍、鬼神、阿須倫王，皆大歡喜樂聞。",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說八吉祥神呪經",
        "from": "T14n0427_001:0073a28_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]